title: Medicare Myths and How to Plan for Coverage
description: MarketWatch reporter Alessandra Malito and Ari Parker, lead adviser at Chapter, discuss Medicare - the misconceptions about the program, the best tips when planning for coverage and what to know about the stability of the program.
